<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>URL Shortener - Welcome</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #1e1e1e;
            color: #f8f8f8;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #000;
            padding: 20px 0;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            z-index: 100;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #d4af37;
        }

        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 30px;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #d4af37;
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
        }

        nav ul li {
            margin-left: 40px;
        }

        .nav-link {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #f8f8f8;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .nav-link:hover {
            color: #d4af37;
        }

        .hero {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 85vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5));
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 0 20px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 60px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 20px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 15px 35px;
            background-color: #d4af37;
            color: #1e1e1e;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 25px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            color: #d4af37;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .features {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            background-color: #2c2c2c;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-top: -30px;
        }

        .feature {
            max-width: 300px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px;
            background-color: #333;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            color: #fff;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .feature:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
        }

        .feature h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #d4af37;
        }

        .feature p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #000;
            color: #d4af37;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 50px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        footer p {
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 45px;
            }

            .hero p {
                font-size: 18px;
            }

            .btn {
                padding: 12px 30px;
                font-size: 18px;
            }

            .features {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }

            .feature {
                max-width: 80%;
                margin: 15px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            header {
                padding: 15px 0;
            }

            .logo {
                font-size: 22px;
            }

            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 35px;
            }

            .hero p {
                font-size: 14px;
            }

            .btn {
                padding: 10px 20px;
                font-size: 16px;
            }

            .feature h2 {
                font-size: 20px;
            }

            .feature p {
                font-size: 14px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <nav>
            <div class="logo">URL Shortener</div>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/login" class="nav-link">Login</a></li>
                <li><a href="/signup" class="nav-link">Sign Up</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Shorten Your Links with Ease</h1>
            <p>Transform your long URLs into short, shareable, and trackable links in an instant. Join the revolution in link management.</p>
            <a href="/" class="btn">Get Started</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
        <div class="feature">
            <h2>Fast & Reliable</h2>
            <p>Experience instant URL shortening and get access to reliable, fast redirection. Never worry about your links again!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <h2>Track Clicks in Real-Time</h2>
            <p>Gain insights into your audience’s behavior. Track the number of clicks on each shortened URL and analyze performance.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <h2>Customizable Links</h2>
            <p>Create branded links with your own custom aliases. Make your URLs more memorable and recognizable for your audience.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <h2>Enhanced Security</h2>
            <p>All your data is encrypted, and we maintain strict privacy standards. Feel confident knowing your information is protected.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>© 2025 URL Shortener. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
